                    We eliminate busywork and focus on the 20% of activities that produce 80% of the results in your job search.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="border border-orange-500/20 bg-orange-500/5 p-4">
                  <h3 class="text-orange-400 font-semibold mb-2">Community Driven</h3>
                  <p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Get support, accountability, and insider knowledge from peers who are on the same journey and mentors who've made it.
